<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Lixp的Blog</title><link>https://golixp.github.io/</link><description>Recent content on Lixp的Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2024 Lixp. [CC BY-SA 4.0](http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/)</copyright><lastBuildDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 13:48:57 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://golixp.github.io/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Ubuntu的Docker容器和镜像消失</title><link>https://golixp.github.io/posts/linux/ubuntu%E7%9A%84docker%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E5%92%8C%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1/</link><pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 13:48:57 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://golixp.github.io/posts/linux/ubuntu%E7%9A%84docker%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E5%92%8C%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1/</guid><description>&lt;p>一次ubuntu Linux机器内存溢出强行重启机器, 启动后docker的容器和镜像全部消失, 后台还有容器相关进程在运行, apt重装docker, 容器和镜像全部都能看到了, 然后在某次正常重启后, 又消失了, 网上查询了很多方式, 都不行, 最后发现是因为snap安装的docker和apt安装的docker共存导致的.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>屏蔽部分GPU</title><link>https://golixp.github.io/posts/linux/%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BD%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86gpu/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 14:41:21 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://golixp.github.io/posts/linux/%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BD%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86gpu/</guid><description>&lt;p>使用&lt;code>lspci | grep NVIDIA&lt;/code>查看:&lt;/p>
&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code>3b:00.0 VGA compatible controller: NVIDIA Corporation Device 2684 (rev a1)
3b:00.1 Audio device: NVIDIA Corporation Device 22ba (rev a1)
5e:00.0 VGA compatible controller: NVIDIA Corporation Device 2684 (rev a1)
5e:00.1 Audio device: NVIDIA Corporation Device 22ba (rev a1)
86:00.0 VGA compatible controller: NVIDIA Corporation Device 2684 (rev a1)
86:00.1 Audio device: NVIDIA Corporation Device 22ba (rev a1)
af:00.0 VGA compatible controller: NVIDIA Corporation Device 2684 (rev a1)
af:00.1 Audio device: NVIDIA Corporation Device 22ba (rev a1)
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;p>或者&lt;code>nvidia-smi&lt;/code>查看:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Btrfs + Grub2 报错: error: Unknown Filesystem. Grub Rescue></title><link>https://golixp.github.io/posts/grub2%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 23:21:30 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://golixp.github.io/posts/grub2%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>&lt;p>开机报错:&lt;/p>
&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code>error: unknown filesystem.
grub rescue&amp;gt;
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;p>无法进入系统引导页面, 这是grub恢复模式.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>使用&lt;code>ls&lt;/code>查看磁盘, 会出现:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>部署使用redis</title><link>https://golixp.github.io/posts/service/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8redis/</link><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:58:28 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://golixp.github.io/posts/service/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8redis/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">docker run -p 6379:6379 --name redis -d redis
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Ubuntu系统NVIDIA驱动和CUDA安装</title><link>https://golixp.github.io/posts/linux/ubuntu%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9Fnvidia%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8%E5%92%8Ccuda%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 16:25:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://golixp.github.io/posts/linux/ubuntu%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9Fnvidia%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8%E5%92%8Ccuda%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</guid><description>&lt;p>使用Ubuntu官方仓库安装:&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>sudo ubuntu-drivers autoinstall&lt;/li>
&lt;li>重启&lt;/li>
&lt;li>sudo apt install nvidia-cuda-toolkit&lt;/li>
&lt;li>sudo apt install nvidia-container-toolkit / sudo apt install nvidia-docker2&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>这种方式比传统的去NVIDIA官网下载&lt;code>.run&lt;/code>文件安装更简单, 并且仓库源由Ubuntu官方维护, 兼容性错误更少&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>MySQL安装相关</title><link>https://golixp.github.io/posts/service/mysql%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 16:25:07 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://golixp.github.io/posts/service/mysql%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group">安装
